## ğŸ¯ Option 2: Full Setup with Testing (10 minutes)

### Complete Installation

```bash
# 1. Clone
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd cybernauts-assignment

# 2. Backend setup
cd cybernauts-backend
npm install
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your MongoDB URL

# 3. Frontend setup
cd ../cybernauts-frontend
npm install
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with VITE_API_URL

# 4. Run tests
cd ../cybernauts-backend
npm test

# 5. Start backend
npm run dev

# 6. Start frontend (new terminal)
cd ../cybernauts-frontend
npm run dev
```

